<div class="elmiron">
  <div class="sec1">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="txt">
        <h1>If you have experienced vision problems after taking the drug <b>Elmiron</b> (used to treat interstitial cystitis), you may be entitled to compensation!</h1>
        <h2>Fill out the form below for a free case evaluation.</h2>
        <div class="title-line"></div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>

        <!-- <h3>Are you injured from an accident in Mobile, Alabama?<br> Contact Injury Attorney Noel B. Leonard today, to discuss your options.</h3> -->
